arts.ttl: Roma Outcast Edging Closer to Joining Fenerbahce
arts.sum: Fringe Roma defender Mario Hermoso is reportedly on the verge of joining Turkish Super Lig colossi Fenerbahce. According to Calciomercato, negotiations between the two clubs are ongoing, with Jose Mourinho eager to take the Spaniard to Istanbul.
